keyPolicies.policyTitle: A job for everyone in Broxtowe.
keyPolicies.policyDescription: We have record levels of employment and apprenticeships in Broxtowe. A strong economy also pays for great services like our NHS.

keyPolicies.policyTitle: The best schools for all our children.
keyPolicies.policyDescription: Broxtowe's schools keep on getting better! Labour were wrong to close academies which have brought aspiration and success.

keyPolicies.policyTitle: Keep on defending our Green Belt.
keyPolicies.policyDescription: Broxtowe is a great place to live and we need our green open spaces not just as places to enjoy but to keep communities special.
